HEADWORD: Gentilism
<hw>Gen"til*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>gentilisme</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Hethenism; paganism; the worship of false
gods.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Tribal feeling; devotion to one's
<xex>gens</xex>.</def></p>

